text: Bayrakatuba () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilchimbetovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 101 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Tuymazy, 3 km from Ilchimbetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Bayrakatuba
